headline: Fastenal Company Announces Conference Call to Review 2025 Second Quarter Earnings
summary: WINONA, Minn., June 26, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq:FAST) ('Fastenal', 'we', 'our', or 'us') announced the date and time for its conference call to review 2025 second quarter results, as well as current operations. The conference call will be broadcast live over the Internet on Monday, July 14, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. central time.
